{"tid":752971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【神棍扮神醫】眼神能醫百病？ 強國「催眠大師」被揭呃逾5百萬","createTime":"2018-07-23T08:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T09:25:28.000Z","uid":83125,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c4d21e4177e88b56362b305bd31aa1cbdcb6d91f","tid":752971,"uid":83125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:45:36.000Z","msg":"內地有催眠大師聲稱可「聚集超強宇宙能量」、「用一個眼神醫百病」、「30秒內能將人催眠成鋼板」，令啞巴開口說話、植物人都可走路，你相信世間上真有此人嗎？內地就有一千多名來自全國各省的人信了，而且還乖乖合共交上了500萬人民幣（下同，約578萬）醫藥費。這名「催眠大師」為了塑造自己的神聖形象，還不惜拍自傳造勢，以騙更多急於求診的病人。不過，她周四（19日）被內媒起底，踢爆騙子的真面目。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「催眠大師」捨棄原名「邱翠雲」，以「邱瀚民」一名行走江湖。宣傳片中的邱瀚民瞄眉畫眼，紅衣烈烈，配搭一頭從後梳的短髮，平時出入乘坐紅色法拉利跑車，住高級酒店，塑造出自己的女強人形象，加強「大師」的可信度，這吸引了來自江蘇、從小患有腦癱的22歲男子小于（化名）的目光。<br />\n<br />\n小于多年來四處求醫，始終未見效果，在網上看到自稱是全球唯一眼神催眠的創始人「邱瀚民大師」的故事，能夠把宇宙能量瞬間植入人體醫治百病，便嘗試向大師求醫。小于說：「當時她給我看的影片裏面，有個啞巴本來不能說話，經過她的治療我就被打動了，當時相信她啊，因為她說得很真」，在邱的游說下，先後付了共1.6萬元（約1.8萬港元），接受眼神催眠治療，不過始終不見果效，小于還被邱罵得狗血淋頭，指他在治療中「不投入」，令邱發功無效。小于接受多次治療後，才驚覺受騙。<br />\n<br />\n江蘇泰州警方接到小于報案後展開調查，發現邱瀚民背後，有一個由30多人組成、分工鮮明的詐騙集團。邱女不但出錢拍自傳電影《神眼穿梭》，還自編自導自演，假扮接受內地知名媒體包括央視、騰訊等訪問，就連她「催眠講課會」上幫忙起哄的參加者，其實都是邱女的同黨，務求將邱女捧上神聖的地位，美言她是「頂尖中的頂尖，大師中的大師，NO.1當中的NO.1」，令更加多人受騙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方表示日前在昆山一場「催眠講課會」現場，拘捕邱女及其他21名疑犯，並揭發各地受騙的患者近千人，被騙資金已超過500萬元人民幣。警方提醒，這些所謂的「超能量」、「超能力」治病方法，都是明顯違背自然科學，奉勸病患和家屬千萬不要因急於治病，墮入詐騙陷阱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/164328_f7c1f40064b3920b70fbe591a3df6f5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F164328_f7c1f40064b3920b70fbe591a3df6f5c.png&h=1efd9579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n強國「催眠大師」斂財$578萬。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/164441_8374eace44971830091985b907f45093.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F164441_8374eace44971830091985b907f45093.png&h=7aa696c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上流出邱女治療病人時情況。"},{"pid":"0ca30da2daf14eebb024e1ef279352848818eee8","tid":752971,"uid":83125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98046858e9bd2672c62e53a94548189970cc648c","tid":752971,"uid":83125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ad47d466b996401ef3de564462e0a3989828ab","tid":752971,"uid":157138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:49:20.000Z","msg":"眼神醫病 幾撚on9先會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5579126a33742920af570d435b47391fcf8436c","tid":752971,"uid":83125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0ad47d466b996401ef3de564462e0a3989828ab","tid":752971,"uid":157138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:49:20.000Z","msg":"眼神醫病 幾撚on9先會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:50:11.000Z","msg":"支那人有正常嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72bdd0cb4a5917976747cf9ca32bb6824eeaedb","tid":752971,"uid":83125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721d3fb9abf3f1ed111e38ec8f82b49d80e874d2","tid":752971,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:05:41.000Z","msg":"有無片睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d4b675af055c68253f77109249a95d28ad65f2","tid":752971,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f8765d645aab21d0e2e3cd4193ce54f13ecf4e","tid":752971,"uid":2545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:09:41.000Z","msg":"d宣傳相又影得幾好<br />\n個look都唔錯，夠哂似神棍，個頭gel到有幾高得幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bed5860a078a6456a5003b94b29f07554899818","tid":752971,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:14:06.000Z","msg":"人類傳心師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f82d179ce0edbb13bf5ea6be179d34b809e7d8","tid":752971,"uid":83125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"721d3fb9abf3f1ed111e38ec8f82b49d80e874d2","tid":752971,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:05:41.000Z","msg":"有無片睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:25:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180722/20457044\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180722%2F20457044&d=dhnmO4SUVKWMyUZrxg720XIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=87a2ab27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180722%2F20457044&h=01c66014\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180722/20457044</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}